Because of this we need to do separate calls for each page we're exporting.

Please see attached image.  This happens intermittently, and (I think) only when navigating to a page with the back button.  Please note the url being used to load the macro.  This is the url we define for the custom macro editor.  This snapshot is from one of our development instance, but we recently had a user report this exact same issue through our support.



